1. Market Information Encoder (MIE) encodes the news text and price features. In this part, an LLM-based Denoised News Encoder is proposed;   
2. Lag-dependent Temporal Causal Discovery (Lag-dependent TCD) module leverages variational inference to mine the causal relationship based on the given market information of stocks, i.e., modeling $p\left(G\mid X_{<T}\right)$ ;   
3. Functional Causal Model (FCM) generates the prediction of future price movements according to the discovered causal graph, i.e., modeling $p\left(\pmb{y}_{T}\mid\pmb{X}_{<T},\pmb{G}\right)$ .

$$
\begin{array}{r l}&{\log p_{\theta}\left(y_{T}\mid X_{<T}\right)=\log\displaystyle\int_{G}\frac{q_{\phi}\left(G\right)}{q_{\phi}\left(G\right)}p_{\theta}\left(y_{T}\mid X_{<T},G\right)p\left(G\right)d G}\\ &{\ge\displaystyle\int_{G}q_{\phi}\left(G\right)\log p_{\theta}\left(y_{T}\mid X_{<T},G\right)p\left(G\right)d G+H\left(q_{\phi}\left(G\right)\right)}\\ &{\ge E_{q_{\phi}\left(G\right)}[\log p_{\theta}\left(y_{T}\mid X_{<T},G\right)+\log p\left(G\right)]+H\left(q_{\phi}\left(G\right)\right)}\\ &{\ge E_{q_{\phi}\left(G\right)}\left[\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{D}\log p_{z_{i}}\left(z_{T}^{i}\right)+\log p\left(G\right)\right]+H\left(q_{\phi}\left(G\right)\right).}\end{array}
$$

$$
\begin{array}{c}{{B C E\left(g_{T},y_{T}\right)=-\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{D}\left(g_{T}^{i}\log\left(y_{T}^{i}\right)+\left(1{-}g_{T}^{i}\right)\log\left(1{-}y_{T}^{i}\right)\right)}}\\ {{\mathcal{L}=\displaystyle\frac{1}{D}\left({-}E L B O+\lambda B C E(g_{T},y_{T})\right)}}\end{array}
$$
